.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-8-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, juice, tea
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, fishing, skydiving
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, firefighter, police-officer
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: fantasy, mystery, spy
There are 3 different nationalities: american, italian, russian
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: gospel, soul, salsa
 1. the person drinking juice is the person who's hobby is baking##1
 2. the firefighter is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person watching fantasy movies is the fan of salsa##1
 4. the fan of soul is not to the right of the russian##8
 5. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the left of the fan of salsa##5
 6. the italian is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
 7. the person watching spy movies is not to the right of the russian##8
 8. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the right of the firefighter##5
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the russian##3
10. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
11. the fan of gospel is on the left of the accountant##1
12. the person who's hobby is baking is not to the left of the person drinking juice##8
13. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the right of the italian##5
14. the accountant is the russian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |       3        |
| Beverage          | tea | juice       | hot-chocolate         |
| Hobby         | fishing     | baking     | skydiving      |
| Job           | firefighter | accountant | police-officer |
| Movie-Genre   | spy         | mystery    | fantasy        |
| Nationality   | italian     | russian    | american       |
| Music-Genre         | gospel    | soul       | salsa          |

