 4. the thai is the person watching musical movies##1
 5. the person watching satire movies is not the person who's sport is rowing##6
 6. the person traveling to edinburgh is not to the left of the person who's sport is rowing##8
 7. the person eating artichoke is not to the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##8
 8. the owner of the goldfish is the thai##1
 9. the person eating artichoke is not the person who's sport is rowing##6
10. the person eating artichoke is somewhere to the right of the person watching family movies##5
11. the person eating kiwi is not the person who's sport is lacrosse##6
12. the egyptian is on the left of the italian##1
13. the person traveling to boston is in the middle##1

